{"tid":1820914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港街馬清晨舉行　張建宗致辭　跑手叫反修例口號","createTime":"2020-01-11T22:12:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T01:01:18.000Z","uid":125193,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4615fa92af75c9c014c9a0d94f0cc05ea3f87b49","tid":1820914,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:12:57.000Z","msg":"香港街馬清晨舉行，是自上年6月反修例風波以來，首次有大型運動項目舉行。清晨5時許，32.195公里組在東區走廊起跑，政務司司長擔任主禮嘉賓。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗致辭時說，在現時環境能舉行街馬，有賴主辦單位上下一心。致辭其間，有跑手報以噓聲，又大叫「五大訴求、缺一不可」口號。有跑手經過主禮台時，舉起示威手勢和標語，亦有人喊「香港人加油」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502316-20200112.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502316-20200112.htm&d=E2fLMnMY5FLAMirJUdBaWWHyg7b2nkJB6fx123wLmsI%3D&h=40a6b33c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1502316-20200112.htm&h=87af2f7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1502316-20200112.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fccebf37256524410bd9ff81a43d53231b1d329d","tid":1820914,"uid":125193,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:19:03.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，決一不可"},{"pid":"b9179ec97059f1e279c69dc8a29fe96e1ed5a05a","tid":1820914,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:20:21.000Z","msg":"好柒凍"},{"pid":"ecd8b74b289ecd9a49a6761e1ba0b1488cddd8e5","tid":1820914,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:44:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca07939859732cfbf1d2e1e59adf75eab393b084","tid":1820914,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9179ec97059f1e279c69dc8a29fe96e1ed5a05a","tid":1820914,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-11T22:20:21.000Z","msg":"好柒凍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-12T01:01:18.000Z","msg":"香港濕凍"}]}